cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.MM

This paper deals with image categorization and sub-categorization using web images and general corpus information. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves text processing and classification, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper deals with information retrieval (IR) and machine learning (LG), which are relevant sub-categories. Finally, the paper involves multimedia (MM) processing, which is another possible sub-category.
